high_descs: go forward to brown coffee table with watch
pick up watch furthest from box on coffee table
turn left, go to black round table with lamp to the left
place watch to the right of keys on round table
turn around, go to coffee table with box
pick up watch next to box on coffee table
turn right, go left past coffee table to black round table to the right
place watch on top of keys on round table

high_descs: cross the room and turn right and go to the coffee table
pick up the watch sitting on the coffee table
turn around and cross the room to the end table beside the couch
place the watch on the table in front of the light
turn around and cross the room back to the coffee table
pick up the watch on the coffee table
cross the room back to the end table
place the watch on the table beside the other watch

high_descs: Walk forward then turn to your right to face the black coffee table.
Pick up the watch closest to you on the coffee table.
Turn to your left and walk to the round black table in the corner by the chair.
Put the watch on the round table near the keys.
Turn around and walk back toward the coffee table, turn to your right, then left and walk between the coffee table and the sofa. Turn to face the coffee table.
Pick up the other watch from the coffee table.
Turn around and walk back to the round black table in the corner by the chair.
Put the second watch on the round table near the other watch.
anns.task_desc: Put two watches near the keys on the round black table in the corner.
